HEADWORD: Whipster
<hw>Whip"ster</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Whip</ets> +
<ets>-ster</ets>.]</ety> <def>A nimble little fellow; a
whippersnapper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Every puny <qex>whipster</qex> gets my sword.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whipstick</ent>⟦br⟧
